      "property-filter": {
        "name": "filter",
        "in": "query",
        "required": false,
        "description": "A filter query string narrows search results and supports the combination of logical and comparison operators. The filter adheres to the pattern filter='field' comparisonType 'value'.\n\nThere are eight comparison types that can be used in filter expressions:\n* equal: eq\n* not equal: ne\n* greater than: gt\n* greater or equal: ge\n* less than: lt\n* less than or equal: le\n* starts with: sw\n* contains a value: contains\n\nThe following fields are filterable:\n* id (eq|ne)\n* name (eq|ne|sw|contains)\n* code (eq|ne)\n* brand.id (eq|ne|contains)\n* chain.id (eq|ne)\n* created (eq|ne|lt|le|gt|ge)\n* lastModified (eq|ne|lt|le|gt|ge)\n",
        "schema": {
          "type": "string",
          "example": "code eq ABC123"
        }
      },
      "property-room-filter": {
        "name": "filter",
        "in": "query",
        "required": false,
        "description": "A filter query string narrows search results and supports the combination of logical and comparison operators. The filter adheres to the pattern filter='field' comparisonType 'value'.\n\nThere are eight comparison types that can be used in filter expressions:\n* equal: eq\n* not equal: ne\n* greater than: gt\n* greater or equal: ge\n* less than: lt\n* less than or equal: le\n* starts with: sw\n* contains a value: contains\n\nThe following fields are filterable:\n* id (eq|ne)\n* name (eq|ne|sw|contains)\n* code (eq|ne)\n* property.id (eq|ne)\n* created (eq|ne|lt|le|gt|ge)\n* lastModified (eq|ne|lt|le|gt|ge)\n",
        "schema": {
          "type": "string",
          "example": "code eq dlx"
        }
      },
